    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开启奇妙冒险</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/bb5ae7fc937a97bcda97a833ef5bdc0b.poster.avif?t=1730145664\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/bb5ae7fc937a97bcda97a833ef5bdc0b.webm?t=1730145664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/bb5ae7fc937a97bcda97a833ef5bdc0b.mp4?t=1730145664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>运用能力，在永无止尽的发现旅程中按照自己的意志操控并改变脚下的土地。通过勘探、战斗、采矿、制作和建造掌控世界。收获作物、驯服野兽、酿造灵药、烹调食物并打造工程机械奇景。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>深入广袤的开放世界</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/35a6b39eec2b030f275d970626e48e6a.poster.avif?t=1730145664\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/35a6b39eec2b030f275d970626e48e6a.webm?t=1730145664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/35a6b39eec2b030f275d970626e48e6a.mp4?t=1730145664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>跨越广袤且令人神往的大自然环境，发现各种奇异的生物。深入层次多样，独特又暗藏危机的地下生物群落，要在此生存绝非易事。掌控世界规律，包括日／夜循环、温度、气候、水、物材、环境成长和繁衍生息。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一起玩耍</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/627fac53d745d0b503b00d28afcac3d6.poster.avif?t=1730145664\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/627fac53d745d0b503b00d28afcac3d6.webm?t=1730145664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/627fac53d745d0b503b00d28afcac3d6.mp4?t=1730145664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>打造你自己的世界并邀请好友或前往公众世界，与新的玩家碰面。轻松浏览上千名线上玩家的世界，前往作客或把它当成自己的家。加入我们日益繁荣且热情好客的社区，结交朋友、获得灵感并学习 Creativerse 所有的秘密。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>创造你的杰作</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/cee5431f7b1903e2e3f83aa08cd0ccec.poster.avif?t=1730145664\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/cee5431f7b1903e2e3f83aa08cd0ccec.webm?t=1730145664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/cee5431f7b1903e2e3f83aa08cd0ccec.mp4?t=1730145664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>搬动并堆砌砖块，以各种不同材料建造并装饰。从逐步引导的蓝图开始或使用超过 400 种不同材料从头打造。熟练操控无线机器并设定多种复杂的交互作用，如生成生物、控制方块、对话、自订检查点和许多功能，创造自己专属的冒险旅程。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与全世界分享</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/ee61e5cc8b1901cc565b8712cd46bdbc.poster.avif?t=1730145664\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/ee61e5cc8b1901cc565b8712cd46bdbc.webm?t=1730145664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/280790/extras/ee61e5cc8b1901cc565b8712cd46bdbc.mp4?t=1730145664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>向上百万其他的 Creativerse 玩家公开自己的创作和冒险旅程。浏览并经历社区上千个亲手打造的体验。收集足够的赞和点击数，让它登上首页！<strong>你有办法创造出最受欢迎的体验吗？</strong>",
